            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Browse our library of professionally designed templates or start from scratch with a blank canvas.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full gradient-bg flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-black mx-auto mb-6">2</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Customize with AI</h3>
