            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Export & Deploy</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Download as MJML, HTML, or Blade template. Integrate directly into your Laravel application.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
