        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">Join thousands of developers creating beautiful, high-converting emails with the power of AI and Laravel.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="https://templates.laravelmail.com/templates" class="px-8 py-3 gradient-bg rounded-xl text-white font-bold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">Browse Templates</a>
