          <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">See what our community has to say</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/[0.06]">
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm">"Laravel Mail saved us hundreds of hours. The AI assistant is incredibly smart and the MJML export works perfectly with our Laravel codebase."</p>
