          <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/[0.06]">
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm">"The template library is massive and the quality is top-notch. We've seen a 40% increase in email open rates since switching."</p>
